<!doctype html>

<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{config.title}}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{config.description}}">
    <meta name="author" content="{{config.author}}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header class="bg-green-500 text-white p-5">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold">{{config.title}}</h1>
            <nav>
                <ul class="flex space-x-4">
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-green-200">Profile</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="bg-green-100">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-800">Bem vindo ao Comida da Boa</h2>
            <p class="text-green-700 mt-4">Um site onde vais encontrar comida da boa. Sem publicidade estranha, sem
                videos aleatórios e sem ter que fazer scroll a página inteira para encontrar os ingredientes</p>
        </div>
    </div>



    <div class="flex justify-center items-center mt-8">
        <div class="flex border-2 border-green-500 rounded">
            <input type="text" class="px-4 py-2 w-full" placeholder="Search for recipes...">
            <button class="flex items-center justify-center px-4 border-l">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                        d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
                </svg>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="mt-8 container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-36 h-36 mx-auto">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/144" alt="Grilled Cheese Sandwich"
                        class="object-cover w-36 h-36">
                </div>
                <div class="p-4">
                    <a href="#" class="text-lg text-green-800 hover:text-green-600">Grilled Cheese Sandwich</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-36 h-36 mx-auto">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/144" alt="Classic Tomato Soup" class="object-cover w-36 h-36">
                </div>
                <div class="p-4">
                    <a href="#" class="text-lg text-green-800 hover:text-green-600">Classic Tomato Soup</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-36 h-36 mx-auto">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/144" alt="Chocolate Brownies" class="object-cover w-36 h-36">
                </div>
                <div class="p-4">
                    <a href="#" class="text-lg text-green-800 hover:text-green-600">Chocolate Brownies</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Add more items here -->
        </div>
    </div>







    <footer class="bg-green-800 text-white mt-12 py-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <p>Thank you for visiting Comida Da Boa</p>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2">Made with <a href="https://www.prandium.com"
                    class="underline text-green-200 hover:text-green-100">Prandium</a></p>
        </div>
    </footer>



    <hr>
</body>

<style>
    :root {
        --bg-color: #ffffff;
        --bg-secondary-color: #f3f3f6;
        --color-primary: #14854F;
        --color-lightGrey: #d2d6dd;
        --color-grey: #747681;
        --color-darkGrey: #3f4144;
        --color-error: #d43939;
        --color-success: #28bd14;
        --grid-maxWidth: 120rem;
        --grid-gutter: 2rem;
        --font-size: 1.6rem;
        --font-color: black;
        --font-family-sans: sans-serif;
        --font-family-mono: monaco, "Consolas", "Lucida Console", monospace;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 720px;
    }

    .search {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }
</style>

</html>